{"tid":2107759,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"劉鑾雄發聲明　指和太太絶無以任何形式支持社運","createTime":"2020-07-14T05:46:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T06:09:56.000Z","uid":151196,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"cd5f73a4166c73e0cac218b518be7cc66818787f","tid":2107759,"uid":151196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T05:46:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/GettyImages-496900088_mjZ3o_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FGettyImages-496900088_mjZ3o_1200x0.png&h=52b83dce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前網上流傳太陽城集團涉洗黑錢被中國當局調查，又指控集團資助香港社會運動，行政總裁周焯華昨日發片澄清，指網上傳言荒謬，但傳言未有平息，且有更多人捲入；華人置業前主席劉鑾雄今天發表聲明，指他和太太陳凱韻「絕對沒有」直接或間接，牽涉以任何形式支持社會運動，近日在香港和澳門的傳媒報道及傳聞「全屬虛構捏造」，他保留法律追究權利。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示自己與太太「生於斯、長於斯，一直愛國愛港」，在目前艱難時刻希望各界團結一致，亦希望傳媒公正持平，避免「誤導或惡意詆毀」的報道。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8A%89%E9%91%BE%E9%9B%84%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E-%E6%8C%87%E5%92%8C%E5%A4%AA%E5%A4%AA%E7%B5%B6%E7%84%A1%E4%BB%A5%E4%BB%BB%E4%BD%95%E5%BD%A2%E5%BC%8F%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E7%A4%BE%E9%81%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258A%2589%25E9%2591%25BE%25E9%259B%2584%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%2598%258E-%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%2592%258C%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E7%25B5%25B6%25E7%2584%25A1%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%25BD%25A2%25E5%25BC%258F%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E9%2581%258B%2F&d=nqzd6QM3TLyrPp4uhCfCn8fSVjQS2PdSygdC4qSdyAU%3D&h=cb375c60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258A%2589%25E9%2591%25BE%25E9%259B%2584%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%2598%258E-%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%2592%258C%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E7%25B5%25B6%25E7%2584%25A1%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E4%25BD%2595%25E5%25BD%25A2%25E5%25BC%258F%25E6%2594%25